
{ Adding a reference to the VBA Extensibility library

  This reference is for example required so that the constants `vbext_ct_StdModule` and `vbext_ct_ClassModule` are known.

  In → Microsoft/Office/Excel[Excel]:
code {
thisWorkbook.VBProject.references.addFromGuid _
        GUID   :="{0002E157-0000-0000-C000-000000000046}", _
        major  :=  5,                                      _
        minor  :=  3
code }

  See also → Microsoft/Office/Visual-Basic-Editor/Object-Model[VB Editor Object Model]

}

sa:
  → Windows/development/COM/Useful-object-libraries
